<section id="type">
  <title><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>codeType<?oxy_custom_end?>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?>[NOTE: should split into
    two files: codeType and mrkType]<?oxy_custom_end?></title>
  <para>codeType - indicates the type of an element.</para>
  <para><emphasis>Type:</emphasis><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>
    string.<?oxy_custom_end?></para>
  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> allowed values for this attribute depend on the
    element in which it is used.</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>When used in <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc">
          <code>&lt;pc&gt;</code>
        </olink>, <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc">
          <code>sc</code>
        </olink>, <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec">
          <code>ec</code>
        </olink> or <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ph.xml" targetptr="ph">
          <code>ph</code>
        </olink>:</para>
      <para>The value  <glossterm>must</glossterm> be set to one of the following values:</para>
      <simplelist>
        <member><code>"fmt"</code> - Formatting (e.g. a &lt;b&gt; element in HTML)</member>
        <member><code>"ui"</code> - User interface element</member>
        <member><code>"quote"</code> - Inline quotation (as opposed to a block citation)</member>
        <member><code>"link"</code> - Link (e.g. an &lt;a&gt; element in HTML)</member>
        <member><code>"image"</code> - Image or graphic</member>
        <member><code>"other"</code> - Type of element not covered by any of the other top-level
          types.</member>
      </simplelist>
      <para><emphasis>Example:</emphasis>
        <programlisting><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,198,140"?>
&lt;segment&gt;
  &lt;source xml:lang="cs">&lt;pc type="quote"><foreignphrase lang="cs">Blázen,
      chce dobýt točnu v takovém počasí&lt;/pc>, dodal slovy svého
      oblíbeného imaginárního autora.</foreignphrase>&lt;/source>
  &lt;target xml:lang="en">&lt;pc type="quote">Madman, he wants to conquer the
      pole in this weather&lt;/pc&gt;, offered he the words of his
      favourite imaginary playwright.&lt;/target&gt;
&lt;/segment&gt;<?oxy_custom_end?>
</programlisting>
      </para>
      <para>One can further specify the type of a code using the <olink targetdoc="subtype.xml" targetptr="subtype">
          <code>subType</code>
        </olink>
      attribute.</para>
      <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> Undefined.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>When used in <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk">
          <code>&lt;mrk&gt;</code>
        </olink> or <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sm.xml" targetptr="sm">
          <code>sm</code>
        </olink>:</para>
      <para>One of the following values: <code>"generic"</code>, <code>"comment"</code>,
          <code>"term"</code>, or a user-defined value that is composed of a prefix and a sub-value
        separated by a character <code>:</code> (U+003A).</para>
      <para>The prefix is a string uniquely identifying a collection of sub-values for a specific authority.
        The sub-value is any string value defined by the authority.</para>
      <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis>
        <code>"generic"</code>.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>When used in <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group">
          <code>group</code>
        </olink> or <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit">
          <code>unit</code>
        </olink>:</para>
      <para>A value that is composed of a prefix and a sub-value
        separated by a character <code>:</code> (U+003A).</para>
      <para>The prefix is a string uniquely identifying a collection of sub-values for a specific authority.
        The sub-value is any string value defined by the authority. The prefix <code>xlf</code> is reserved.</para>
      <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> Undefined</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/group.xml" targetptr="group">
      <code>group</code>
    </olink>, <olink targetdoc="../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit">
      <code>unit</code>
    </olink>, <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
      targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc">
      <code>pc</code>
    </olink>,<?oxy_custom_end?>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc">
      <code>sc</code>
    </olink>, <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec">
      <code>ec</code>
    </olink>, <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
      targetdoc="../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk">
      <code>&lt;mrk&gt;</code>
    </olink>,<?oxy_custom_end?>
    <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ph.xml" targetptr="ph">
      <code>ph</code>
    </olink> and <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sm.xml" targetptr="sm">
      <code>sm</code>
    </olink>.</para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Processing Requirements</title>
    <listitem>
      <para><firstterm>Modifiers</firstterm> updating the <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>property<?oxy_custom_end?>
        <link linkend="type">
          <code><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>codeType<?oxy_custom_end?></code>
        </link> on <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
          targetdoc="../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc">
          <code>&lt;pc&gt;</code>
        </olink>,<?oxy_custom_end?>
        <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc">
          <code>sc</code>
        </olink>, <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec">
          <code>ec</code>
        </olink>, or <olink targetdoc="../elements/inline/ph.xml" targetptr="ph">
          <code>ph</code>
        </olink>
        <glossterm>must</glossterm> also update or delete <olink targetdoc="subType.xml"
          targetptr="subtype">
          <code>subType</code>
        </olink>.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
